            <title>[DERBY-2440] DerbyNetNewServer should specify port when it starts a server to avoid requiring 1527 to run</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2440</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To make it possible to run several JUnit tests suites concurrently on &lt;br/&gt;
the same machine, this test should consult TestConfiguration.getCurrent().getPort()&lt;br/&gt;
when starting the servers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;DerbyNetNewServer is currently being run as part of NetHarnessJavaTest via&lt;br/&gt;
the old harness adapter HarnessJavaTest.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
